data.description: Beautiful hilltop Hillsborough home with a magical view of the valleys with over 3000 sf. with 4 large bedrooms and 2  & 1/2 baths. This unique property features a huge master suite downstairs with a roomy closet, jetted tub and walk-in shower along with granite flooring. 3 bedrooms upstairs with walk-in closets in each of them. A "Hollywood" bathroom upstairs with lots of hardwood cabinetry and storage. Hardwood flooring throughout the downstairs areas. Don't miss the cook's dream kitchen with granite counter tops, a large chef's island and new electric range top and new wall oven with air fryer included.  There are a number of special rooms for all types of uses: piano room, formal dining room, family room. A gas generator on site, new roof in 2018, new water heaters in 2023. You will enjoy sitting on the spacious front porch or the back patio area and deck. See agents remarks!!!
